      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下零售系统的组件依赖关系。核心场景是CouponSystem、PointOfSale、Inventory和OrderManagement四个模块之间的交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
