      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。CustomCli和CustomApp都是CouponSystem的入口，但一个是命令行一个是应用层对吗？然后CustomSdk对应PointOfSale，CustomLib对应Inventory，CustomApi对应OrderManagement？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib",
        "CustomApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个映射关系。方向用LR，从左到右展示依赖流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "direction"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，五个类已经创建，标注了各自的零售子系统。现在处理依赖关系：CustomCli需要同时用到Inventory和PointOfSale的能力，所以用虚线连接CustomLib和CustomSdk。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomLib",
        "CustomSdk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "CustomApp同样依赖PointOfSale，也加上到CustomSdk的虚线。还有，PointOfSale本身也依赖Inventory，CustomSdk要连到CustomLib。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在关键的同步交互：PointOfSale通过HTTP向OrderManagement发请求，这是CouponSystem发起的bRequest消息，需要实线表示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApi",
        "bRequest",
        "HTTP connection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，这里有两个关系：一个是带bRequest的实线关联，另一个是独立的HTTP连接虚线。返回的bResponse消息要单独画，从CustomApi指回CustomSdk。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApi",
        "bRequest",
        "bResponse",
        "HTTP connection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，三条关系：实线去程标bRequest/CouponSystem，虚线标注HTTP connection，返回用开放箭头标bResponse/PointOfSale。OrderManagement和Inventory之间也有依赖吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomApi",
