      "utterance": "全部添加完成。我检查一下：CustomCli和CustomApp都通过using关系连接CustomSdk和CustomLib；CustomSdk和CustomLib互相using；CustomSdk与CustomApi之间有bRequest实线、HTTP虚线、bResponse返回箭头；CustomApi和CustomApp各自using CustomLib。",
